				</div>
				<div class="col-12">
					<p class="sub-heading">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 28. ASSIGNMENT. Subject to the approval of Owner, the Charterer shall have the option of subletting or assigning this Charter to any individual or company, but the 
