				<div class="col-12">
					<p class="sub-heading">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 29. LIBERTY CLAUSES. (a) In any situation whatsoever and wheresoever occurring and whether existing or anticipated before commencement of or during the voyage, which in 
