				</div>
				<div class="col-12">
					<p class="sub-heading">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 31. ARBITRATION. Any dispute arising from the making, performance or termination of this Charter Party shall be settled in New York, Owner and Charterer each appointing an 
